;,\u0026#34;https://jalopnik.com/these-are-the-unbreakable-rules-of-winter-driving-1851208960\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://jalopnik.com/these-are-the-unbreakable-rules-of-winter-driving-1851208960\"\u003ecold here\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e. The wind chill outside my apartment right now is \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://jalopnik.com/just-starting-your-car-in-a-siberian-winter-is-a-multi-1850085656\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://jalopnik.com/just-starting-your-car-in-a-siberian-winter-is-a-multi-1850085656\"\u003ea brisk 26 degrees\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, and last weekend we got down to 25. I, a moron, of course spent that 25-degree day trundling all across Brooklyn on \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://jalopnik.com/my-bmw-f800gs-needs-a-vanity-plate-what-should-i-get-1851423282\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://jalopnik.com/my-bmw-f800gs-needs-a-vanity-plate-what-should-i-get-1851423282\"\u003emy motorcycle\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e with nothing but a leather jacket, heated grips, and Gore-Tex gloves to keep me warm. - Amber DaSilva \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://jalopnik.com/how-im-planning-to-ride-my-motorcycle-through-the-new-y-1851715087\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://jalopnik.com/how-im-planning-to-ride-my-motorcycle-through-the-new-y-1851715087\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"8d878a8fb7ea998f98e6be23903959a0\" data-recommend-id=\"image://8d878a8fb7ea998f98e6be23903959a0\" data-format=\"gif\" data-width=\"920\" data-height=\"518\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"A gif sh